<HL>
   Placer to Boost
   Mine Stake to 50%
   For $211 Million
   ----
   By Larry M. Greenberg
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/13/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C13
</SO>
<CO>
   ICR.A ICRA PDG T.PDG
</CO>
<MS>
BASIC MATERIALS (BSC)
</MS>
